    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of shrub or small tree native to eastern North America, but very uncommon north of the Ohio River; designated as threatened. Found in dry upland habitats.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
